  "rules": [
    "This brand-kit.json is the single source of truth for The Creek brand. AI agents must load and follow these paths, colors, and rules.",
    "Black and white are the primary brand colors — default to these for all generated content. Accent and secondary colors are supporting use only.",
    "Logos must only appear in black or white. Use the dark (black) variant on light backgrounds; the light (white) variant on dark backgrounds.",
    "The horizontal combination mark is always preferred. Use stacked only when horizontal space is limited.",
